<varlistentry id="options.Pad">
	<term>Pad<emphasis remap='I'>[type color]</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>will pad image if it is smaller then screen  with  specified
		color.  Possible type values are :
                1: - pad horizontally and tile vertically
                2: - pad vertically and tile horizontally
                3: - pad both vertically and horizontally to make the image the
		size of the screen.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
